PR description:

Breaks the org_service.py god module (330 lines, 15+ functions) into three focused services: orgs/service.py (member CRUD), admin/service.py (system-admin operations), users/service.py (user lookups + lifecycle). Splits admin routes by sub-domain (org management vs user management). Extracts org-specific dependencies and permissions into orgs/. Uses re-export shims at each commit boundary to keep CI green.